Our apps (iQuran, iPray and iSubha) do
NOT
:
Track you
Know who you are
Store any personal or sensitive information
Pass any personal or sensitive information to any cloud
Show any adverts
Share any details with advertisement companies
Sell or buy anything remotely related to an advert
Our apps
DO
:
Include anonymous crash reporting for streamlining bug reporting and fixing
Include anonymous reporting of certain features used within the app solely for the intention of enhancing user experience in future updates